## Technology Stack and Constraints
### Core Technologies
- React: ^18.2.0
- Vite: ^5.0.0
- Module Federation: ^1.3.3
- TailwindCSS: ^3.3.5
- React Hook Form: ^7.48.2

## Quality Management Protocol
